# PalmCare AI iOS App — Current State

## Architecture
- **SwiftUI** app targeting iOS 16+, built with **XcodeGen** (`project.yml`)
- Bundle ID: `com.palmtechnologies.palmcare`, Team: `QFS97GTYJH`
- API base: configurable via `Info.plist` → `API_BASE_URL`, fallback `https://api-production-a0a2.up.railway.app`
- Auth tokens stored in **Keychain** via `KeychainHelper`

## Key Files
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `Theme/PalmCareTheme.swift` | Brand colors (palmPrimary = teal #0D9488), adaptive dark/light |
| `Services/APIService.swift` | API client with Keychain token storage, `requestVoid` for 204s |
| `Models/Models.swift` | Codable models with `AnyCodable` for flexible JSON |
| `Views/Components/PalmAlert.swift` | Custom branded alert replacing native `.alert()` |
| `Views/Clients/AddClientSheet.swift` | 7-tab client form matching web app |
| `Views/Record/RecordView.swift` | Voice recording orb with mic.fill icon |

## Custom Components
- **PalmAlert**: Use `.palmErrorAlert()` or `.palmConfirmAlert()` — NEVER use native `.alert()`
- **AddClientSheet**: 7-tab form (Personal, Contact, Emergency, Medical, Care Plan, Insurance, Scheduling)
- Tab bar uses `ScrollView(.horizontal)` with `palmPrimary` active state

## Demo Account
- Email: `demo@agency.com`, Password: `demo1234`
