## Build Commands
```bash
cd ios-app && xcodegen generate && xcodebuild -project PalmCareAI.xcodeproj -scheme PalmCareAI -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone 17 Pro' -derivedDataPath build build
```

## Recent Fixes (Feb 22)
- **ClientDetailView**: Emergency contacts use `emergencyContactCard()` — structured multi-line layout with icons
- **VisitDetailView**: Overview tab calls `loadAllTabData()` to eagerly fetch transcript/billables/notes/contract concurrently
- **Contract view**: Properly formatted (was showing raw syntax), 3 previewable style templates
- **Billables view**: Timestamps removed, accept/deny buttons added
- **RecordView**: `MARKETING_DEMO_FLOW` debug flag for automated demo recordings
- **Recording orb**: Uses `mic.fill` icon (NOT waveform — reverted per user request)

## Important Rules
- Always use `Color.palmPrimary`, `Color.palmText` etc. from theme — never hardcode colors
- Use `Color(UIColor.secondarySystemGroupedBackground)` for adaptive backgrounds
- Always add `.accessibilityLabel()` to interactive elements
- Use `@MainActor` for classes with `@Published` properties
- Replace force unwraps with safe optional handling
